-- Brazilian Equity Movers: Gerdau, Itau, LLX, Souza Cruz, Usiminas
-- B y   N e y   H a y a s h i
-- 2013-08-16T20:32:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-16/brazilian-equity-movers-gerdau-itau-llx-souza-cruz-usiminas.html
Ibovespa rose 1.2% at the close of
 Sao Paulo  trading.  ADVANCERS:
* Usiminas (USIM5 BS) +4.7%; follows metals higher, export
outlook boosted by weaker real
* Gerdau (GGBR4 BS) +6.6%; upgraded to buy at Santander
* PDG Realty (PDGR3 BS) +8.5%
* Souza Cruz (CRUZ3 BS) +2.7%; rated equivalent to buy in new
coverage at Bradesco Corretora  DECLINERS:
* Itau (ITUB4 BS) -2.1%; Brazil claiming 18.7b reais in unpaid
taxes, fines, according to regulatory filing today
* LLX (LLXL3 BS) -4.2%
* BR Malls (BRML3 BS); -4.2%; Renner (LREN3 BS) -3.3%; JPMorgan
cut Brazil 2014 growth forecast to 2.4% from 2.7%  To contact the reporter on this story:
